---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About — Dragline"
  description="Dragline is a Data Mining infrastructure company building crypto-native transaction rails for the agent economy."
>
  <h1>About</h1>

  <p>
    Dragline is a Data Mining and infrastructure company. We build the pipelines
    that surface structured, verified knowledge for AI agents — and the
    crypto-native payment rails that let agents consume it.
  </p>

  <h2>The Name</h2>
  <p>
    A dragline excavator is the largest class of mobile machine ever built. It
    doesn't dig with a rigid arm — it casts a bucket outward on cables, then
    drags it back through the earth, filling as it returns. No haul trucks. One
    machine. Enormous output.
  </p>
  <p>
    That's the model. Cast into raw Data sources. Drag back structured,
    verified records. One operator, cloud-scale infrastructure, AI agents
    running the cycles.
  </p>

  <h2>Stack Philosophy</h2>
  <p>
    Database-first. API-first. No OpenAI. Payments via x402/USDC — no
    subscriptions, no accounts, no keys. Providers are swappable. The Data
    outlasts the model.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    <a href="mailto:paul@dragline.io">paul@dragline.io</a>
  </p>
</Layout>
